videos.description: Sviatoslav Mykhailiuk knocks down a 3-pointer giving Kansas a 7-point lead over Omaha.
videos.headline: Mykhailiuk left open for Jayhawk 3

videos.description: Devonte Graham gets left all alone as he hits a deep 3-pointer to put the Jayhawks up 35-21.
videos.headline: Graham knocks down catch-and-shoot 3

videos.description: Devonte Graham forces a steal and hustles down the court to get the lob to Lagerald Vick for the alley-oop.
videos.headline: Graham sets up Vick for the big alley-oop

videos.description: Marcus Garrett gets the offensive rebound out to Devonte Graham who nails a 3-pointer late in the 1st half.
videos.headline: Kansas fires 3 off quick thinking rebound

videos.description: Kansas' Sviatoslav Mykhailiuk gets down the court quickly and hits Udoka Azubuike for the close alley-oop.
videos.headline: Mykhailiuk gets the steal and sets up Azubuike for the oop

videos.description: Sam Cunliffe gives and receives on the alley-oop from Devonte Graham as Kansas continues to run up the score on Omaha.
videos.headline: Cunliffe flies for Kansas alley-oop
